---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
import { business } from '../data/business';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Transparency & Pricing | Healthy Paws Animal Hospital"
  description="Honest, upfront pricing at Healthy Paws Animal Hospital. We discuss costs before treatment, offer in-room checkout, and never surprise you with hidden fees. Lake in the Hills, IL."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-hpah-green-light py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-hpah-green font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Transparency & Pricing</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-6">Honest Conversations About Cost</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-hpah-text-light">
        We believe you deserve to know what veterinary care costs before we provide it — not after.
        At Healthy Paws, financial transparency is a core value, not an afterthought.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl mb-6">Our Transparency Philosophy</h2>
      <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Veterinary care shouldn't come with financial anxiety. Too many pet owners have experienced the stress of
        not knowing what a visit will cost until they're standing at a checkout counter, caught off guard by a total
        they didn't expect. We built Healthy Paws to work differently.
      </p>
      <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        From the moment we discuss your pet's health needs, we include cost as part of the conversation — openly and
        without judgment. We believe informed pet owners make better decisions, and that starts with understanding
        the financial investment alongside the medical recommendation.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-hpah-bg-warm rounded-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-hpah-green">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-hpah-text mb-2">Our promise to you:</p>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
          We will always discuss costs before treatment. We will always explain what you're paying for and why.
          And we will always respect your decisions about your pet's care, regardless of budget.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-hpah-bg-warm">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl mb-10 text-center">How We Handle Pricing</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Costs Discussed First</h3>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
            Before we perform any procedure, run any diagnostic, or administer any treatment, our veterinarians
            discuss the expected cost with you. You'll know what to expect before we proceed — every time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Written Estimates</h3>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
            For procedures, surgeries, and treatment plans, we provide detailed written estimates so you can review
            everything at your own pace. If anything changes during treatment, we contact you before proceeding.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">In-Room Checkout</h3>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
            Your visit ends in the privacy of the exam room — not at a public front desk. Payment, scheduling, and
            any questions about costs happen in a comfortable, private space where you can speak freely.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">No Hidden Fees</h3>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
            The price we discuss is the price you pay. There are no surprise charges, administrative fees, or
            unexplained line items on your invoice. What we quote is what we charge.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Ranges -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl mb-4">Common Service Pricing Ranges</h2>
      <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-8">
        While every pet's needs are unique — and final pricing depends on species, size, age, and specific health
        conditions — these ranges give you a general idea of what to expect. We're happy to provide a specific
        estimate for your pet during a consultation.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Comprehensive Wellness Exam</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light">Annual or semi-annual physical examination</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-hpah-green font-bold whitespace-nowrap ml-4">Starting from $65</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Core Vaccinations</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light">Individual vaccine pricing varies by type</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-hpah-green font-bold whitespace-nowrap ml-4">$25 - $55 each</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Dental Cleaning</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light">Includes anesthesia, scaling, polishing, and dental radiographs</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-hpah-green font-bold whitespace-nowrap ml-4">$400 - $800+</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Spay / Neuter</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light">Varies by species, size, and age</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-hpah-green font-bold whitespace-nowrap ml-4">$300 - $600+</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Bloodwork Panel</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light">CBC, chemistry, and other diagnostics</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-hpah-green font-bold whitespace-nowrap ml-4">$150 - $350</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Sick Visit / Urgent Care</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light">Exam plus diagnostics and treatment as needed</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-hpah-green font-bold whitespace-nowrap ml-4">$85 - $300+</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-6 italic">
        These are approximate ranges provided for planning purposes. Actual pricing depends on your pet's individual
        needs. We always provide a specific estimate before proceeding with any services.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value vs Price -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-hpah-bg-warm">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl mb-6">Why We Focus on Value, Not Lowest Price</h2>
      <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        We understand that cost matters — it's one of the reasons we're so transparent about it. But we also believe
        that the cheapest veterinary care isn't always the best veterinary care. At Healthy Paws, our pricing reflects
        the quality of medicine we practice.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light"><strong>Longer appointments</strong> — our doctors spend 30+ minutes per visit, not 10</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light"><strong>Low-stress protocols</strong> — every visit includes gentle handling and stress-reduction techniques that take additional time and training</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light"><strong>Modern diagnostics</strong> — in-house lab work means faster answers and earlier interventions</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light"><strong>Personal follow-ups</strong> — Dr. Burgess calls after surgeries and significant procedures</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light"><strong>Education-first approach</strong> — you leave every visit understanding more about your pet's health</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-hpah-text-light mt-6 leading-relaxed">
        When you compare the depth of care, the time spent with your pet, and the personal attention you receive,
        you'll find that Healthy Paws delivers exceptional value. We'd rather help fewer pets exceptionally well
        than many pets rushed through a revolving door.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Insurance & Payment -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl mb-6">Insurance & Payment Options</h2>

      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Pet Insurance</h3>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          We strongly encourage pet owners to consider pet insurance. While we are not affiliated with any specific
          insurance provider, most major pet insurance companies work on a reimbursement model — you pay at the time
          of service and submit claims directly to your insurer for reimbursement.
        </p>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light leading-relaxed">
          We're happy to provide the detailed invoices, medical records, and documentation your insurance company
          needs to process claims. If you're unsure whether pet insurance is right for you, ask us during your next
          visit — we can discuss what to look for in a plan based on your pet's age, breed, and health history.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-10">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Accepted Payment Methods</h3>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-4">Payment is due at the time of service. We accept:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-hpah-text-light">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            Cash and personal checks
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            Visa, MasterCard, Discover, American Express
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            CareCredit (financing with flexible payment plans)
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Questions About Cost?</h3>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-4">
          If you're concerned about the cost of a recommended treatment, please say so. We genuinely want to help
          you make the best decision for your pet within your means. We can discuss alternatives, prioritize
          treatments, or develop a phased plan that spreads costs over time.
        </p>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
          Call us at <a href={`tel:${business.phoneRaw}`} class="text-hpah-green font-semibold hover:underline">{business.phone}</a> or
          email <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`} class="text-hpah-green font-semibold hover:underline">{business.email}</a>
          with any pricing questions before your visit.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Links -->
  <section class="py-12 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Related Pages</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/policies/" class="text-hpah-green hover:underline text-sm">Hospital Policies</a>
        <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
        <a href="/why-choose-us/" class="text-hpah-green hover:underline text-sm">Why Choose Us</a>
        <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
        <a href="/wellness-exams-lake-in-the-hills-il/" class="text-hpah-green hover:underline text-sm">Wellness Exams</a>
        <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
        <a href="/schedule/" class="text-hpah-green hover:underline text-sm">Schedule a Visit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA />
</BaseLayout>
